.SH "NAME"
icv \- Convert images to and from various formats
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBicv\fP [\-h] [\-i \fIfile\fP] [\-\-input\-format \fIfmt\fP] [\-o \fIfile\fP] [\-\-output\-format \fIfmt\fP] [\-w \fIwidth\fP] [\fIinput_file\fP] [\fIoutput_file\fP]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBicv\fP is a tool to convert images to and from a variety of image
formats.  Currently support formats include:
.sp
.it 1 an-trap
.nr an-no-space-flag 1
.nr an-break-flag 1
